bool POIInfo::load (  const MC2String &  filename,
uint32  offset
) 
 

Load POI information from a file.

This will load all static data. The dynamic data has to be loaded seperatly if needed ( the holdsDynamicInfo() indicates if it holds dynamic data in a database ).

Parameters:
filename the file to load from
offset the offset in the file
Returns:
true of information was loaded successfully
